<div class="og-builder">
  <section class="enter-url">
    <header class="row">
      <h1 class="large-12 columns">
        <span>1</span>
        Paste in a URL
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="field large-12 columns">
        <input
          type="url"
          @keyup.13="handleURLReturn"
          @click="handleURLClick"
          v-model="url"
          :readonly="url != '' && title"
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div v-if="loading" class="loading" transition="slide">
      Just a second, we're crunching some bitsâ€¦

      <loader></loader>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div v-if="!loading && url && title !== null" transition="slide">
    <section class="customize">
      <header class="row">
        <h1 class="large-12 columns">
          <span>2</span>
          We made our best guess. Now you can set it up <em>just right</em>
        </h1>
      </header>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="columns medium-10 medium-centered large-8 large-uncentered">
          <image-preview :url="facebookImageURL"></image-preview>
        </div>

        <div class="columns large-4">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="field columns small-6 medium-4 large-12">
              <label for="ogImageURL">Image URL</label>
              <input id="ogImageURL" type="url" v-model="ogImageURL">
            </div>

            <div class="field columns small-6 medium-4 large-12">
              <label for="logoURL">Logo URL</label>
              <input id="logoURL" type="url" v-model="logoURL">
            </div>

            <div class="field columns medium-4 large-12">
              <label>Accent Color</label>
              <color-picker-input :color.sync="accentColor"></color-picker-input>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="field small-6 medium-4 large-2 columns">
          <label for="textPosition">Text Position</label>
          <select v-model="textPosition" id="textPosition">
            <option value="top">Top</option>
            <option value="middle">Middle</option>
            <option value="bottom">Bottom</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="field small-6 medium-4 large-2 columns">
          <label for="textAlignment">Text Alignment</label>
          <select v-model="textAlignment" id="textAlignment">
            <option value="left">Left</option>
            <option value="center">Center</option>
            <option value="right">Right</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="field small-6 medium-4 large-2 columns">
          <label for="fontFamily">Font Family</label>
          <select v-model="fontFamily" id="fontFamily">
            <option value="Avenir Next Demi,Bold">Avenir</option>
            <option value="DIN Alternate,Bold">Din</option>
            <option value="Charter">Charter</option>
            <option value="Georgia">Georgia</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="field small-6 medium-4 large-2 columns">
          <label>Text Color</label>
          <color-picker-input :color.sync="textColor"></color-picker-input>
        </div>

        <div class="field small-6 medium-4 large-2 columns">
          <label for="logoAlignment">Logo Alignment</label>
          <select v-model="logoAlignment" id="logoAlignment">
            <option value="top,left">Top left</option>
            <option value="top,center">Top center</option>
            <option value="top,right">Top right</option>
            <option value="bottom,left">Btm left</option>
            <option value="bottom,center">Btm center</option>
            <option value="bottom,right">Btm right</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="field small-6 medium-4 large-2 columns">
          <label for="logoPadding">Logo Padding</label>
          <input type="number" v-model="logoPadding">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="start-sharing">
      <header class="row">
        <h1 class="large-12 columns">
          <span>3</span>
          Start sharing!
        </h1>
      </header>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="small-8 small-centered medium-4 medium-uncentered large-4 columns">
          <image-preview :url="fullImageURL"></image-preview>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-8 large-8 columns">
          <div class="field">
            <input type="text" class="final-url" v-model="fullImageURL" readonly @click="selectFullURL">
          </div>

          <p>This URL can be used to replace your page's existing <code>og:image</code> content, or shared directly anywhere on the internet. If you integrate it into your page using the <code>og:image</code> tag, this dynamic image will show up whenever people share your page on sites like Facebook or Twitter, and automatically tweak its layout to fit each platform.</p>

          <p>If you're replacing the <code>og:image</code> of a dynamic website, you can simply swap out the <code>url</code> and <code>image_url</code> query string parameters of the generated URL on each page, just make sure to URL encode them! the title of each unique page will be pulled in automatically.</p>

          <p>If you have any questions or thoughts, we'd love to hear from you on <a href="https://twitter.com/imgix">Twitter</a>, or in <a href="http://slack.imgix.com">our community Slack</a>.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
